<link>https://the-decoder.com/claude-code-runs-a-github-repos-hidden-malware-without-verification-giving-attackers-full-control/</link>
<guid isPermaLink="false">https://the-decoder.com/?p=37141</guid>
<pubDate>Mon, 29 Jun 2026 10:04:32 +0000</pubDate>
<source>the-decoder.com</source>
<description><![CDATA[【the-decoder.com】Mozilla 0DIN平台的安全研究人员展示了，一个被攻陷的GitHub仓库如何在Claude Code等AI编码工具运行其设置时，立即接管开发者的机器。关键在于：恶意代码仅在运行时通过DNS查询加载，在仓库中、对扫描器以及AI代理本身均不可见。本文《Claude Code runs a GitHub repo's hidden malware without verification, giving attackers full control》最初发表于The Decoder。<br/><br/><a href="https://the-decoder.com/claude-code-runs-a-github-repos-hidden-malware-without-verification-giving-attackers-full-control/">阅读原文</a>]]></description>
